enforcement agents are not required to register weapons but he 
insisted that only those individuals are allowed to use the weapons 
lee added that it is a violation of law for other family members 
even to touch an agents weapon 
the fbi does not require agents to register with local 
authorities weapons used for official duties according to ray 
mcelhaney an fbi spokesman he declined to say whether a 
22caliber revolver the weapon used in the shooting would 
normally be approved for use by fbi agents 
