chicken soup 
a typical 7ounce portion of dried soup contains 726 
milligrams of sodium and the samesized bowl of canned soup 
contains 850 milligrams of sodium while our frozen just what the 
doctor ordered soup contains 22 milligrams of sodium patrick 
ascolese food services manager at the hospital said monday 
