circulated in portauprince 
aristide who preaches that marxism and christianity are 
compatible has not actually called for an armed uprising but 
repeatedly advocated the overthrow of the lt gen henri namphys 
military government by active nonviolent struggle 
the conservative hierarchy of the church has rejected aristides 
