exchange them for mohammed 
schmidt an engineer was freed sept 7 1987 
in bonn a west german government spokesman who demanded 
anonymity said he knew of no deal with iran or with the kidnappers 
for cordes freedom the government has repeatedly denied it paid a 
ransom for schmidts release 
